{"tid":1852990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩唔該儘量慳住使","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T19:06:18.000Z","uid":65045,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"93a5c7bd4d824e28366be2db76746b68dfc184ac","tid":1852990,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"當香港人每人每日剩係用一個口罩<br />\n一個月嘅消耗量都講緊超過4百萬盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以的話請大家儘量少啲出街<br />\n屋企一次買多幾日餸，放假減少gathering <br />\n就算屋企有2-3個月嘅存貨，都幫幫手一齊減少demand <br />\n每個香港人落少次街已經慳到十幾萬盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慳啲用一來可以畀其他有需要嘅人大啲機會買到<br />\n二來未來疫情唔知發展成點，其他國家嘅supply始終唔穩定 <br />\n三來消耗咁多口罩都幾唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a3a83d3c871986d908ae785b7b0108a767d3e4","tid":1852990,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0f2e2473e9da1dd697e83a55dc50dee1f20c24e","tid":1852990,"uid":95138,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"拎黎保命你同我講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e75a196a09965a9e4a31cf6214515b05eaa382","tid":1852990,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:20:13.000Z","msg":"你死撚左就最環保"},{"pid":"f4c76b1d46e1dcbcb185a4529307e03300cf49a0","tid":1852990,"uid":49336,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"本來成篇文都正正常常<br />\n<br />\n睇到最尾嗰句屌出嚟<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦講環保 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地球人類死曬最環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時冇人需要消耗口罩"},{"pid":"15b6bde2fa652c3ea553dcdf099e2465ec5e2b89","tid":1852990,"uid":278038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"1日用1個算啦<br />\n1日4個真係唔好講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875ed835087d1e5d981f8289b3843ed58ac086ce","tid":1852990,"uid":141419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"用完唔好掉<br />\n收集好送去南邊圍<br />\n做人要環保<br />\n反正入面有藍絲派口罩俾同胞<br />\n人哋要做好心實唔夠貨<br />\n我哋香港人最鍾意幫人"},{"pid":"2123075f483723ccf83a0629617ab0038cbf7c8e","tid":1852990,"uid":65045,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰句派膠的<br />\n當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f1a49f4d695f5d97e7c0988663856af41e9442","tid":1852990,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:23:40.000Z","msg":"想環保咪清蒸口罩囉"},{"pid":"406415b63d44b2c3ec0ab29824ab2fa145c1011a","tid":1852990,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c76b1d46e1dcbcb185a4529307e03300cf49a0","tid":1852990,"uid":49336,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"本來成篇文都正正常常<br />\n<br />\n睇到最尾嗰句屌出嚟<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦講環保 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地球人類死曬最環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時冇人需要消耗口罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"地球或成最後贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194f03e28546ec078fa268da42e2beb35d9e5037","tid":1852990,"uid":136702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"重用好過啦 又環保又唔洗搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e08ce130e1e1a65de5c132a35c59ae04a3afc26","tid":1852990,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"出少啲街消費啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77801462d26bb1c8f3facef72c91f53524a229f","tid":1852990,"uid":111105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"中國口罩產量佔全球一半，你為什麼還買不到口罩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1852678/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1852678/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n//目前口罩日產量至少有800萬 2月底我國將日產各類口罩近1.8億隻//<br />\n我睇到個po嘗試計下幾時大家先夠口罩用<br />\n拋個磚出黎想睇下有冇高手計準啲<br />\n有好多因素都冇計到<br />\n啲人唔出街 醫護用多幾倍 海外又會增產<br />\n好粗略就咁當每月增加1.72億日產量<br />\n3月 1.80億<br />\n4月 3.72億<br />\n5月 5.24億<br />\n6月 6.96億<br />\n7月 8.68億<br />\n8月 10.40億<br />\n9月 12.12億<br />\n10月 13.84億<br />\n要去到10月先達到中國人口每人一日一個<br />\n如果疫情一直持續 會唔會係去到10月先夠口罩?"},{"pid":"25f1f339cc9384c391553349c3d66a6c5497f90d","tid":1852990,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"無必要唔好去人多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152608d29c0ae7c604eb8d6d9787b00df730200","tid":1852990,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"除左返工已經唔出街，真係無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f53ed4ed818e4b0d51b78d72ced6b2e496a8dc","tid":1852990,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"唔環保點持續發展？<br />\n成班反上腦<br />\n出去拎多幾支飲管啦<br />\n點柒知m記就中資嘅<br />\n7仔 kfc就怡和 撐警奶共嘅<br />\n真係報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dce653de21e1f68eb5919e44da742f514202e70","tid":1852990,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:36:17.000Z","msg":"睇頭兩句已知你想講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真 你癮撚咗最環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e37efb3d6a7056d518a87519ebffe985c416e6","tid":1852990,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"通常人地叫我慳我就會用多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bbb1431e3f012ba2f4240790ec1dd0f979cee0","tid":1852990,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"啲廢老死晒最環保<br />\n所以唔好比口罩比佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bff570ea5a2c7e6d2e9ae739d205dc4453301a","tid":1852990,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:06:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=15ab4781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=2f33ed33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D1123